{"lemma":"رِباُ","slug":"رِباُ","root":"ر.ب.#","root_slug":"ر-ب-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ب-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رِبا","root":"ربو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":7},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14408","n14617","n14623"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%A8%D8%A7%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"interest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"usury, usurious interest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"gain in selling, profit"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to grow"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to increase"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare Hebrew ריבית (ribít, “interest”).\n\nCompare Hebrew רָבַב (rabab, “to be many, to multiply, to increase”)."},"ipa":["/ri.baː/","/ra.baː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14408","headword_ar":"رَبَاَ","root":"rbA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabo'N","text_ar":"رَبْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) [or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, high,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated, so as to overtop,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"overlook, what was around"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"adjacent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtbA^","text_ar":"ارتبا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^ati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"رَبَاَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabo'N","text_ar":"رَبْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground rose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some read, in the Kur xxii. 5 and xli. 39,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^ato","text_ar":"رَبَاَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabato","text_ar":"رَبَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; because, as Zj says, when a plant is about to appear, the earth rises thereat. (M, TA.) And you say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a EalaY jabalK","text_ar":"رَبَاَ عَلَى جَبَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtbA^","text_ar":"ارتبا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArbA^","text_ar":"اربا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took a high and commanding position upon a mountain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascended upon it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orafa Ealayoh","text_ar":"اَشْرَفَ عَلَيْه"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to look."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA Earafotu fulaAnFA","text_ar":"مَا عَرَفْتُ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY","text_ar":"لِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hat~aY A^arobaA^a","text_ar":"حَتَّى اَرْبَاَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I knew not such a one until he became within a commanding,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"near, view of me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a$orafa","text_ar":"اَشْرَفَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a EalaY $arafK","text_ar":"رَبَاَ عَلَى شَرَفٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ascended upon an eminence"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to watch"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lest an enemy should come unawares upon a party."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^otu AlmarobaA^apa","text_ar":"رَبَاْتُ المَرْبَاَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotabaA^otuhaA","text_ar":"اِرْتَبَاْتُهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ascended upon the place of observation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a Alqawoma","text_ar":"رَبَاَ القَوْمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, K, *) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabo'N","text_ar":"رَبْءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^alahumo","text_ar":"رَبَاَلَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, M, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirotabaA^ahumo","text_ar":"اِرْتَبَاَهُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted as,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a scout to the party,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, * K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon an eminence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a lanaA fulaAnN","text_ar":"رَبَاَ لَنَا فُلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ArtbA^","text_ar":"ارتبا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"acted as, a scout to us."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^otu bika Eano ka*aA","text_ar":"رَبَاْتُ بِكَ عَنْ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. and inf. n. as above, means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exalted thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"held thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above such a thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^otu bika A^arofaEa AlA^amori","text_ar":"رَبَاْتُ بِكَ اَرْفَعَ الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I exalted thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the highest degree"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IJ, M:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^otu binafosiY","text_ar":"رَبَاْتُ بِنَفْسِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano Eamali ka*aA","text_ar":"عَنْ عَمَلِ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I held myself above the doing such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Har p. 265:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~iY laA^arobaA^u bika Eano h`*aA","text_ar":"اـِنِّى لَاَرْبَاُ بِكَ عَنْ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amori","text_ar":"الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily I exalt thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hold thee"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above this thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Har ubi suprà, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and do not approve of it for thee:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har, TA:) as though properly signifying I betake myself with thee to an elevated place of observation, in honour of thee, and in care, or solicitude, for thee, and preserve thee and keep watch for thee as a scout and a watchman: (Har ubi suprà:) [this usage of the verb, as is shown in the TA, is what is meant by its being said that]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a","text_ar":"رَبَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rafaEa","text_ar":"رَفَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a AlmaAla","text_ar":"رَبَاَ المَالَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He preserved, guarded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took care of,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and put into a good,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  See also 3. ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^a fiY AlA^amori","text_ar":"رَبَاَ فِى الاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He looked into the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, and considered."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA^otu fiyhi","text_ar":"رَبَاْتُ فِيهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to Fr, means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealimotu Eilomahu","text_ar":"عَلِمْتُ عِلْمَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I knew his knowledge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he knew;"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I tried, proved,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tested, him, and so knew what he knew"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA. [See the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA^a xoburan~a xabaraka","text_ar":"لَاَ خْبُرَنَّ خَبَرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA rabaA^a raboA^ahu","text_ar":"مَا رَبَاَ رَبْاَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not know,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had no knowledge of, nor did he desire, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not know,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had no knowledge of, and did not prepare himself for, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not care for, mind, heed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regard, him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA rabaA^otu rabo'a fulaAnK","text_ar":"مَا رَبَاْتُ رَبْءَ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did not know such a one, nor care for, mind, heed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"regard, him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K. *)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaw^uwA lahu","text_ar":"رَبَوُوا لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They collected for him of every kind of food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, *)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"milk and dates &c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a yarobaA^o fiY","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ يَرْبَاْ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mi$oyatihi","text_ar":"مِشْيَتِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came bearing himself heavily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sluggishly, in his gait."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K. * [Like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yaronaA^u","text_ar":"يَرْنَاُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A4-  See also what next follows."}],"source_refs":["K","M","TA","IJ","Har","Lh","T"]},{"entry_id":"n14617","headword_ar":"رَبَا","root":"rbw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarobuw","text_ar":"يَرْبُو"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabowN","text_ar":"رَبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so in copies of the S, [in one of my copies of the S not mentioned,]) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubuw~N","text_ar":"رُبُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA='N","text_ar":"رَبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K, TA,) the latter erroneously written in [some of] the copies of the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaA='","text_ar":"رِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a thing, T, S, Msb)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"increased,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"augmented."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Msb, K.) Said, in this sense, of property: (Mgh:) or, said of property,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It increased by usury."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liyarobuwa fiY A^amowaAli A@ln~aAsi falaA yarobuw","text_ar":"لِيَرْبُوَ فِى اَمْوَالِ ا@لنَّاسِ فَلَا يَرْبُو"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA A=tayotumo","text_ar":"وَمَا ا=تَيْتُمْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einoda A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"عِنْدَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xxx. 38], (T, Bd,) means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And what ye give of forbidden addition in commercial dealing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of usury,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Bd,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what ye give of anything for the sake of receiving more in return,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Zj, T, Bd,) and this is not forbidden accord. to most of the expositions, though there is no recompense [from God] for him who exceeds what he has received, (Zj, T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that it may increase the possessions of men,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, * Bd,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it shall not increase with God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Bd,) nor will He bless it: (Bd:) some (namely, the people of El-Hijáz, T, or Náfi' and Yaakoob, Bd) read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liturobuwA","text_ar":"لِتُرْبُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, Bd,) meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that ye may increase"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the property of men"},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that ye may have forbidden addition"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"usury therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Bd.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It became high."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, * TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA","text_ar":"رَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor. as above; and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiYa","text_ar":"رَبِىَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarobaY","text_ar":"يَرْبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; said of a child,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He grew up."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabawotu fiY","text_ar":"رَبَوْتُ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baniY fulaAnK","text_ar":"بَنِى فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Hajorihi","text_ar":"فِى حَجْرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubuw~N","text_ar":"رُبُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubowN","text_ar":"رُبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) with damm, (TA,) this latter on the authority of Lh, (M, TA,) accord. to the K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabowN","text_ar":"رَبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with fet-h, but correctly with damm; (TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiytu","text_ar":"رَبِيتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, TA,) in the copies of the K erroneously written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabayotu","text_ar":"رَبَيْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA='K","text_ar":"رَبَا=ءٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubiY~N","text_ar":"رُبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, K, TA; [the latter, accord. to the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabiY~N","text_ar":"رَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is a mistranscription;])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I grew up"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among the sons of such a one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his care and protection"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, M, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabati","text_ar":"رَبَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ground"},{"kind":"text","text":"[being rained upon]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became large, and swelled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA.) In the Kur xxii. 5 and xli. 39, for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warabato","text_ar":"وَرَبَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", some read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warabaA^atN","text_ar":"وَرَبَاَتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": the former means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"becomes large, and swells;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"increases:"},{"kind":"text","text":"the latter means “ and rises. ” (T. [See art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rbA^","text_ar":"ربا"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA Als~awiyqu","text_ar":"رَبَا السَّوِيقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubuw~N","text_ar":"رُبُوٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swyq","text_ar":"سويق"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meal of parched barley"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"had water poured upon it, and in consequence swelled:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA:) in the copies of the K,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA Als~awiyqa","text_ar":"رَبَا السَّوِيقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he poured water on the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"swyq","text_ar":"سويق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it consequently swelled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabaA","text_ar":"رَبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a horse, (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yarobuw","text_ar":"يَرْبُو"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabowN","text_ar":"رَبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became swollen,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inflated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"from running, or from fear, or fright (S, K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabowN","text_ar":"رَبْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, K;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, out of breath; his breath became interrupted"},{"kind":"text","text":"by reason of fatigue or running &c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he panted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breathed shortly"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uninterruptedly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ainobahara","text_ar":"اِنْبَهَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"trb~Y","text_ar":"تربّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; for you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TalabonaA AlS~ayoda Hat~aY tarab~ayonaA","text_ar":"طَلَبْنَا الصَّيْدَ حَتَّى تَرَبَّيْنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We pursued the chase until"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"we became out of breath;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buhironaA","text_ar":"بُهِرْنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) ―         -b8-  See also 4.       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rabawotu","text_ar":"رَبَوْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~aAbiyapa","text_ar":"الرَّابِيَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I ascended,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mounted, upon the hill,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","TA","Mgh","Bd","Zj"]},{"entry_id":"n14623","headword_ar":"رِبًا","root":"rbw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, M, Msb, K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFwA","text_ar":"رِبًوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh,) [for it is often thus written, and generally thus in the copies of the Kur-án,] with the short"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to the pronunciation best known, (Msb,) [which implies that it is also pronounced ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaA='N","text_ar":"رِبَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An excess,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an addition:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an addition over and above the principal sum"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is lent"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expended"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: but in the law it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an addition obtained in a particular manner:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) [i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"usury,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning both"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"unlawful,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lawful, interest"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"practice of taking such interest"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] it is in lending, (Zj, T,) or in buying and selling, (S,) and in giving: and is of two kinds; unlawful, and lawful: the unlawful is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any loan for which one receives more than the loan,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by means of which one draws a profit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"gain made by such means:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and the lawful is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift by which a man invites more than it to be given to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a gift that he gives in order that more than it may be given to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"addition that he so obtains:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Zj, T:) [it generally means]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an addition that is obtained by selling food"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for food"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ready money for ready money, to be paid at an appointed period;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by exchanging either of such things for more of the same kind:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd in ii. 276:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking of an addition in lending and in selling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(PS:) [it is said to be]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiynapN","text_ar":"عِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (M, K:) [but although"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFA","text_ar":"رِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiynapN","text_ar":"عِينَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are both applicable sometimes in the same case, neither of them can be properly said to be generally explanatory of the other, or syn. therewith:"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaA Aln~asiyoy^api","text_ar":"رِبَا النَّسِيْيَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a term specially employed to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit obtained in the case of a delay of payment:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribaA AlfaDoli","text_ar":"رِبَا الفَضْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"profit obtained by the superior value of a thing received over that of a"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1024},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing given:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the dual of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFA","text_ar":"رِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFwA","text_ar":"رِبًوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribawaAni","text_ar":"رِبَوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribayaAni","text_ar":"رِبَيَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, M, Msb, K;) the former being agreeable with the original; (M, Msb;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the latter being because of the imáleh occasioned by the preceding kesreh. (M.) See an ex. near the beginning of the first paragraph of this art. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruboyapN","text_ar":"رُبْيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", thus pronounced by the Arabs, but by the relaters of a trad., in which it occurs, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~iy~apN","text_ar":"رُبِّيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, T, S, Mgh,) or, as some say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubay~apN","text_ar":"رُبَيَّةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", as though this were the dim. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruboyapN","text_ar":"رُبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) is a dial. var. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFwA","text_ar":"رِبًوا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ribFA","text_ar":"رِبًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and by rule should be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rubowapN","text_ar":"رُبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Fr, T, S, Mgh:) or, accord. to Z,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rub~y~apN","text_ar":"رُبّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may be of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlapN","text_ar":"فُعُّولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~ibaA","text_ar":"الرِّبَا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramaA='N","text_ar":"رَمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rmY","text_ar":"رمى"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["T","M","Msb","K","S","Mgh","Zj","PS","Fr"]}]}}